# AkhAI Web Interface - Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env.local and add your API keys

# ============================================
# AI Provider API Keys (ALL REQUIRED)
# ============================================

# Anthropic Claude (Mother Base + Redactor)
# Get your API key from: https://console.anthropic.com/
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# DeepSeek (Advisor Slot 1 - Technical Brainstormer)
# Get your API key from: https://platform.deepseek.com/
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=sk-...

# xAI Grok (Advisor Slot 2 - Strategic Brainstormer)
# Get your API key from: https://console.x.ai/
XAI_API_KEY=xai-...

# OpenRouter (Advisor Slot 3 - Diversity Brainstormer)
# Get your API key from: https://openrouter.ai/keys
# Note: Uses Google Gemini Pro 1.5 by default
OPENROUTER_API_KEY=sk-or-v1-...

# ============================================
# Optional: Web Search (for future features)
# ============================================

# Brave Search API (Optional)
# Get your API key from: https://brave.com/search/api/
# BRAVE_SEARCH_API_KEY=

# ============================================
# Setup Instructions
# ============================================
# 1. Copy this file: cp .env.example .env.local
# 2. Add your API keys to .env.local
# 3. Restart the dev server: pnpm dev
# 4. Test in the Settings page to verify API keys work
